title: Submachine 9: the temple HD + OST Mateusz Skutnik
description:
Submachine 9: The Temple HD

HD version of a free flash game from Pastel Stories, by Mateusz Skutnik. 

For some reason, the author hasn't realised that in 2014 being able to play in full screen is obligatory and not a paid option. Hopefully, this torrent will fix that. 

Includes:
 - Submachine 9: The Temple for PC and MAC,
 - Original soundtrack (OST) by ThumpMonks
